===簽證===
*持有{{link-en|哥斯大黎加護照|Costa Rican passport}}的{{link-en|哥斯大黎加人口|Demographics of Costa Rica|哥斯大黎加公民}}可以90天免签入境尼加拉瓜<ref>{{Timatic|nationality=CR|destination=NI}}</ref>。

持{{link-en|尼加拉瓜護照|Nicaraguan passport}}的{{link-en|尼加拉瓜人口|Demographics of Nicaragua|尼加拉瓜公民}}必须提前申请签证才能入境哥斯达黎加。<ref>{{Timatic|nationality=NI|destination=CR}}</ref>

2017年哥斯达黎加共接待尼加拉瓜游客429,990人次，尼加拉瓜是哥斯达黎加第二大旅客来源国<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.ict.go.cr/es/estadisticas/informes-estadisticos.html |title= Informes Estadísticos - Anuarios |language= es |website=  |publisher= Instituto Costarricense de Turismo |access-date= 2017-12-11 |archive-date= 2018-03-24 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180324025918/http://www.ict.go.cr/es/estadisticas/informes-estadisticos.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>；而哥斯达黎加则是尼加拉瓜第三大旅客来源国。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.intur.gob.ni/estadisticas-de-turismo/ |title=Estadisticas de Turismo |accessdate=2020-08-27 |archive-date=2020-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200802225811/https://www.intur.gob.ni/estadisticas-de-turismo/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

